align: center;'>$125.00</td>\n<td style='width: 20%; text-align: center;'>$130.00</td>\n<td style='width: 20%; text-align: center;'>$145.00</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style='width: 20%; text-align: center;'>Youth (14-18)</td>\n<td style='width: 20%; text-align: center;'>$50.00</td>\n<td style='width: 20%; text-align: center;'>$50.00</td>\n<td style='width: 20%; text-align: center;'>$50.00</td>\n<td style='width: 20%; text-align: center;'>$69.00</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style='width: 20%; text-align: center;'>Child (0-13)</td>\n<td style='width: 20%; text-align: center;'>N/A</td>\n<td style='width: 20%; text-align: center;'>FREE**</td>\n<td style='width: 20%; text-align: center;'>FREE**</td>\n<td style='width: 20%; text-align: center;'>FREE**</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p><small><i>** Call 1-888 655-9090 to add free Child ticket(s) to your order.</i></small></p>\n\n<table style='width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; border-style: solid;' border='1'>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style='width: 20%; text-align: center;'><b>DAY PASS</b></td>\n<td style='width: 20%; text-align: center;'>Early Bird<br /><small><i>(until December 31)<br /></small></i></td>\n<td style='width: 20%; text-align: center;'>Advance<br /><small><i>(January 1-May 31)<br /></small></i></td>\n<td style='width: 20%; text-align: center;'>Regular<br /><small><i>(until Aug. 14)<br /></small></i></td>\n<td style='width: 20%; text-align: center;'>Gate<br /><small><i>(as of Aug. 15)<br /></small></i></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style='width: 20%; text-align: center;'>Friday</td>\n<td style='width: 20%; text-align: center;'>N/A</td>\n<td style='width: 20%; text-align: center;'>$120.00</td>\n<td style='width: 20%; text-align: center;'>$125.00</td>\n<td style='width: 20%; text-align: center;'>$140.00</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style='width: 20%; text-align: center;'>FLEX (Sat. or Sun.)</td>\n<td style='width: 20%; text-align: center;'>N/A</td>\n<td style='width: 20%; text-align: center;'>$140.00</td>\n<td style='width: 20%; 