    ],
    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "Dancespicable Me"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p><b>Content Warnings: mild flashing lights, use of fog machine, loud music and cheering.</b></p>\n\n<p>When a mysterious villain steals the Great Pyramid of Giza, veteran supervillain Gru is determined to reclaim his title as the greatest villain of all time by pulling off the ultimate heist. With the help of his mischievous Minions, eccentric inventions, and an unexpected group of cookie-selling sisters, Gru sets a bold new plan in motion: to steal the moon.  As his elaborate scheme unfolds through dynamic dance numbers, hilarious mishaps, and over-the-top villainy, Gru finds himself facing an even bigger challenge: learning what truly matters. Follow the NWSS dancers as they take you on an adventure of unexpected friendships and the perfect balance of mischief and heart.  </p>\n\n<p>Run Time 70 minutes with no intermission</p>\n\n<style>\n.location-page-temp {display: block!important;}\n@media screen and (max-width: 600px){iframe{width:100%;}}\n</style>\n"
      }
