    ],
    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "Festival Days Cabaret featuring the Barkells - 18+ Event"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>The Festival Days Cabaret brings the party with live music by The Barkells, plus opening set by Kaeley Jade. Hit the dance floor for a nonstop mix of rock, pop, dance, hip-hop, and country hits from the '70s to today. Add in licensed bar service with a wide range of drink options, happy hour, a photo booth, high-energy vibes, and an optional gourmet burger bar—it's the ultimate night out. PLUS, your ticket = your vote, buy your ticket by May 20 and receive a link to vote on the night's playlist!</p>\n\n\n\n \n\n<p>Cabaret Opener: 7:15 p.m. | <a href='https://kaeleyjade.com/' target='_blank'>Kaeley Jade</a><br>\nCabaret Headliner: 7:45 p.m. | <a href='https://thebarkells.com/' target='_blank'>The Barkells</a></p>\n\n\n\n \n\n<p>Doors: 6 p.m.<br>\nHappy Hour: 6 to 7 p.m.<br>\nOptional Gourmet Burger Bar: 6:30 to 7:30 p.m.</p>\n\n \n\n<p><u>Advance Tickets</u> $30 +GST (April 27 to May 29)<br>\n<u>Regular Tickets</u> $35 +GST (May 30 to June 20)<br>\n\nSelect your seat/table at time of ticket purchase.</p>\n\n \n\n<p>Optional <a href='https://www.morinville.ca/media/wzrhnukq/menu_gourment-burger-bar_cabaret_2026.pdf' target='_blank'>Gourmet Burger Bar</a> $25 +GST<br>\nGourmet Burger Bar only available for purchase at time of ticket purchase.</p>\n<p>Morinville Festival Days, Proud Media Partner: <b><a href='https://www.cfcw.com/' target='_blank'>840 CFCW</a></b></p>\n<p>Morinville Festival Days Proud Media Partners:     <b><a href='https://www.k97.ca/' target='_blank'>K-97</a>  |  <a href='https://www.963thebreeze.com/' target='_blank'>96.3 The Breeze</a>  |  <a href='https://newcountry979.ca/' target='_blank'>New Country 97.9</a></b></p>\n<p><a href='https://www.morinville.ca/festivaldays#collapse_98e500e5-f719-42f3-8578-e635fe9851e5_7' target='_blank'>Morinville Festival Days Weekend Event Schedule</a></p>\n\n<style>\n.location-page-temp {\n    display: block!important;\n}\n</style>\n"
      }
    ],
