    ],
    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "Ho'omaka Hanu A Ke Aloha Dance Society Presents Ho'ike"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p><b>Aloha! Ia Orana!</b></p>\n \n<p>Join us for an unforgettable journey with Ho'omaka Hanu A Ke Aloha's 5th annual Ho'ike (show)! Immerse yourself in the graceful sway of the Pacific, as dancers weave tales of love, legends and the spirit of aloha.</p>\n \n<p>From ancient Hawaiian hula to vibrant beats of modern Tahitian ori, let us transport you to locations and stories of the islands. This is more than a show - it is a cultural journey to paradise!</p>\n \n<p>Hawaiian or Tahitian attire is HIGHLY encouraged! </p>\n \n<p>New this year! We will be hosting a 50/50 draw to help fundraise bringing a Kumu from Hawaiʻi to our community to lead workshops.\nCash only. Tickets sold before the show and during intermission.</p>\n\n\n<style>\n.location-page-temp {\n    display: block!important;\n}\n</style>"
      }
    ],
