        "@value": "<p>Last Birds' intimate, one mic performance style blends contemporary folk and traditional country music. Through haunting vocal harmonies and interwoven acoustic guitars, the duo tells stories of small-town experiences and the challenges of prairie life. Mike Davis and Lindsay Arnold draw audiences into a shared experience with their honest lyrics and authentic spousal banter that is satisfyingly bittersweet, often humorous, and always mesmerizing to watch.</p>\n\n<p>Children 12 and under are free if accompanied by an adult. No ticket required.</p>\n\n<style>\n.location-page-temp {\n    display: block!important;\n}\n</style>"
