    ],
    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "Lynyrd Skynyrd tribute: Symply Skynyrd"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>Welcome to Canada&#39;s premiere Lynyrd Skynyrd tribute: Symply Skynyrd. Symply Skynyrd is a seven-piece tribute band devoted to bringing the music of Lynyrd Skynyrd to fans everywhere.</p>\n\n<p>Comprised of veteran musicians who are fans first, the band is committed to playing the best of Skynyrd for true fans and music lovers of classic rock. From clubs to outdoor festivals, Symply Skynyrd brings the music of Skynyrd alive with lively performances As a Lynyrd Skynyrd Canada tribute we keep it simple - Lynyrd Skynyrd is all we play! From Freebird to Sweet Home Alabama, Symply Skynyrd plays the hits and best-of songs: Call Me the Breeze, Gimme Three Steps, and more.</p>\n\n<p>We play the ballads including Tuesday's Gone, the awesome power ballad Simple Man plus the true fan favorite - The Ballad of Curtis Loew!</p>\n\n\n<style>\n@media screen and (max-width: 600px){\niframe{width:100%;}\n}\n</style>"
      }
    ],
