    ],
    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "Monster Madness"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>Feel the roar of the monster trucks as the Monster Madness CHAMIONSHIPS head to Kawartha Downs in Fraserville ON. Three Champions! Racing - Wheelies - Freestyle. Special guests, the stars from the FMX World Tour! This is an action-packed afternoon fans won't want to miss!</p>\n\n<p>The MONSTER MADNESS TOUR, featuring some of the biggest MONSTER TRUCKS in the industry, will have you on your feet as you watch 10,000 pounds of a monster truck soaring through the air! The competition will include wheelies, racing, monster truck freestyle and more!</p>\n\n<p>The FMX WORLD TOUR act will leave fans and families amazed as death defying stunts only the brave would attempt are performed, inside the arena. FMX World Tour is the perfect blend of athletic ability, extreme stunt competitions and tricks and flips! FMX World Tour stars will perform tricks such as, lazy boy, backflips, seat grabs, cliff hangers, in addition to the infamous kiss of death!</p>\n\n<p><b>VIP TICKETS</b>: Get access to the pre-show VIP Pity Party, receive a souvenir VIP lanyard, plus get early entry to choose your seats first!</p>\n\n<p>Children 2 and UNDER ON LAP ARE FREE<br>\nChildren 12 AND OLDER = ADULT</p>\n\n<style>\n.location-page-temp {display: block!important;}\n.location-event-temp {display: none!important;}\n</style>"
      }
