      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "Monster Madness"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>Feel the roar of the monster trucks as the Monster Madness Tour stops in Owen Sound Ontario at the Owen Sound Fair Grounds with stars from the 'FMX World Tour' and more! This is an action-packed afternoon fans won't want to miss!</p>\n\n<p>MONSTER MADNESS TOUR: Rat Nasty Monster Madness Champion returns with 6 of the biggest Monster Trucks in the world. Including Canada's #1 female Monster Truck SABOTAGE. Monster Madness will have you on your feet as you watch the 10,000 pounds of MONSTER TRUCKS soar through the air! The competition will include tricks like wheelies, racing, monster truck freestyle and more!</p>\n\n<p>FMX WORLD TOUR will leave fans and families amazed as death defying stunts only the brave would attempt are performed, inside the arena. FMX World Tour is the perfect blend of athletic ability, extreme stunt competitions and tricks and flips! FMX World Tour stars will be performing such tricks as, captain morgan, kiss of death, cliff hangers, in addition to the famous BACKFLIP!</p>\n\n<p>PIT PARTY - PIT PARTY FROM 11:00am - 12PM Fans will get a chance to meet the drivers, get up close to the monster trucks, stars of fmx, take pictures and receive autographs. Plus True North the official Monster Madness Ride Truck will be taking part in the pit party. ALL ADVANCE TICKETS INCLUDE FREE PIT PASSES. </p>\n\n<p>PURCHASE TICKET AT <a href='https://www.ticketpro.ca/' target='_blank'>www.ticketpro.ca</a><br>\n<br>\nChildren 2 and UNDER ON LAP ARE FREE<br>\nChildren 12 AND OLDER = ADULT<br>\nFor more details visit <a href='www.monstermadnesstour.ca' target='_blank'>https://www.monstermadnesstour.ca/</a></p>\n\n\n<p><b>TICKET PRICES INCREASE $5.00 July 1st</b></p>\n\n\n                                               <p><b>(Monster Truck line up subject to change without notice)</b></p>\n\n<style>\n.location-page-temp {display: block!important;}\n.location-event-temp {display: none!important;}\n</style>"
      }
    ],
