    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "The Rod Show - The Ultimate Rod Stewart Tribute"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>The ROD Show - Ultimate Rod Stewart Tribute featuring Brad Lovell pays homage to Sir Rod Stewart beloved by fans around the world with the HITS we all know and love- Maggie May, Da Ya Think I'm Sexy?, You're in My Heart, Hot Legs, Forever Young, Some Guys Have All The Luck and so many more.</p>\n\n<p>With their passion, dedication and attention to detail The ROD show - The Ultimate Rod Stewart Tribute will take you on an incredible musical journey, down to Rod's signature raspy voice, iconic clothes and spiky blonde hair that is Ooh La La!</p>\n\n<p>The ROD Show - Ultimate Rod Stewart Tribute is simply the BEST live full concert tribute to legendary Rod Stewart. The show is equipped to succeed. Beyond talented musicians and stage performers. This show is fun, dynamic, and the ultimate trip down memory lane, celebrating the music and spirit of one of the world's highest-grossing recording artists: the iconic Sir Rod Stewart.</p>\n\n<iframe width='560' height='315' src='https://www.youtube.com/embed/zpU1pZJpvxM?si=BAI_ndcrbQPOnCwL' title='YouTube video player' frameborder='0' allow='accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share' referrerpolicy='strict-origin-when-cross-origin' allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n\n<style>\n@media screen and (max-width: 600px){iframe{width:100%;}}\n</style>\n"
      }
